# RFC: {{ title }}

## Summary

This RFC records the original direction of {{ project_name }} — the principle,
idea, and belief the project was seeded with. It is the project's first
evolution event, so the evolution layer is not empty at project birth.

## Motivation

A project that begins from intent needs that intent captured explicitly. Without
an anchoring record, later direction changes cannot be compared against the
original statement, and lifecycle checks have nothing to measure against on day
one.

## Detailed Design

